- `THEME_COLOR_KEYS` array matches the keys of `ThemeColors`
- `fontFamily` and `fontSize` are non-empty strings on every theme

---

## Files to modify/create

| File | Action |
|------|--------|
| `packages/shared/src/themes.ts` | **Create** — theme types, built-in themes, `getTheme`, `listThemes` |
| `packages/shared/src/themes.test.ts` | **Create** — unit tests |
| `packages/shared/package.json` | **Edit** — add `"./themes"` export |
| `apps/web/src/index.css` | **Edit** — add semantic CSS custom properties |
| `apps/web/src/hooks/useTheme.ts` | **Edit** — extend with custom theme support |
| `apps/web/src/components/ThemeSelector.tsx` | **Create** — theme swatch grid component |
| `apps/web/src/routes/_chat.settings.tsx` | **Edit** — wire ThemeSelector into Appearance section |

---

## Verification

1. `bun typecheck` — must pass across all packages
2. `bun lint` — must pass (oxlint)
3. `bun run test` in `packages/shared` — themes.test.ts must pass
4. Manual: open settings page → Appearance → see theme swatches → click "Midnight" → UI turns deep blue-black → click "Light" → UI turns light → click "Dark" → UI turns standard dark
